schema.description:
Custom HTTP header for pagination data. Returns Link and Total-Count data in an easy to read JSON format.
Example:
{
  "totalCount": 49,
  "links": {
      "next": "https://api-test.gateway.equinor.com/maintenance-api/equipment?page=3&api-version=v1",
