schema.description:
Custom HTTP header for pagination data. Returns Link and Total-Count data in an easy to read JSON format.
Example:
{
  "totalCount": 490,
  "links": {
      "next": "https://api-test.gateway.equinor.com/maintenance-api/reports/eqhub-and-semi-usage?page=4&api-version=v1",
      "prev": "https://api-test.gateway.equinor.com/maintenance-api/reports/eqhub-and-semi-usage?page=2&api-version=v1",
      "first": "https://api-test.gateway.equinor.com/maintenance-api/reports/eqhub-and-semi-usage?api-version=v1",
      "last": "https://api-test.gateway.equinor.com/maintenance-api/reports/eqhub-and-semi-usage?page=5&api-version=v1"
  }
}

